### 可视化概览
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化流程列表
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/processes?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化流程详情
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/processes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化实例列表
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/instances?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化实例详情
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/instances/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 校验流程定义
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/processes/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definitionJson": "{ \"nodes\": [], \"edges\": [] }"
}

### 保存流程草稿
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/processes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "sample-flow",
  "definitionJson": "{ \"nodes\": [], \"edges\": [] }"
}

### 发布流程定义
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/processes/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processId": "1",
  "version": 1,
  "note": "demo publish"
}

### 指标聚合
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化审计
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/visualization/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}


